values:
umm yeah you can tell molly wrote that last journal entry for me by the phrases "life is pretty good right now" and "she owes me"

enough said.

yup.. i'm at mols... and i love her to death.. and we've gotten a lot closer lately.. which is awesome. 

i owe her but she owes me like 900$ in gas money.. so we're even haha

yea thats about all.. life is pretty good right.. work isn't bad either.

and peace cause i'm out

umm can i just tell you how much square dancing sucked today because i was in a good group and stuff but then i had to go to the bathroom when people were picking their partners so i definitely got screwed over... oh well better luck on thursday!
yeah it was an uneventful monday-thats for sure.. ok this one will be shorter since the last one was so long

yay! im excited right now because rob burgett got a job at subway because of me! lol and now i will actually have someone to talk to!  because the other girls that work there are all in college and take 50 trillion smoking breaks an hour and are like anti-school so we don't have much in common so i am so excited that rob will be working there now! ok im done.

so this is my good deed for the day......

i was workin at subway (like always) and this old man comes in every Sunday and buys subs for him and his wife and hes like 75 years old.  so it took him at least ten minutes to reach the door then another 20 minutes to reach the counter to tell us his order.  but hes sooo cute with his little cane and how he takes little baby steps.  so he gets his subs and he walking out the door but its like really slippery cuz of the ice and on the way out he went like ten times even slower so i ran outside and i helped him and he was like tugging on my sweatershirt and chattering away to me.  but i was out there for like 20 minutes and of course i didn't put a coat on so yeah im prolly gonna get sick now.  but he made it to his little cute mini van safely so thats all that matters.  and then he gave me a cute little hug! : )
download Jonny Lang right now.  he is awesome.

yeah so it definitely doesn't feel like a saturday... im all screwed up with my days right now.  but anyways last night i ended up going to leaf and bean with christina and i tried this new coffee thing and it was DISGUSTING so i went back up and got a vanilla chai latte (of course).  So I pretty much spent $7 on one good cup of tea- what a disappointment.  Then, we came back here and watched Uptown Girls-which was so cute and we ate this double fudge brownie black forest torte thing my mom made.  It was heavenly.  

So today I am going to the mall with shannon to spend more money and to eat more food and then I hafta work from 4-8:30.  yay.  well im out for now.

OK so I officially love our new superintendent.  Wow- who the heck was Dr. Dadey??  The man of the year is obviously Mr. Stein.  

So anyways I couldn't fall asleep last night so I ended up watching "double back-to-back" episodes of Full House and The Cosby Show on nick at night.  I am such a fanatic for classic television, its crazy.  So yeah now I am figuring out what to do the rest of the day since I have no track meet or school to occupy my day!  everyone enjoy the 5 day weekend!

so i set up this live journal. woo hoo... yeah and today we had  no school even though it was still fine out so that like rocked.  and then we don't have school again on monday! love it.  so today i got up at 7:30 because i am so unable to ever sleep in and i hate it, but i tried so hard. lol and then i ate a lot and watched tv and then i went over to molly's hosue and saw her bunny! how cute and then we like cleaned her house ??? hmmm and then we came back to eat dinna here (everyone had meatballs but i had chicken b/c i don't want to get mad cow disease) and then we tried to learn how to belly dance from this tape i have.. haha good times. 

 and i was watching friends and it reminded me of that song Pheobe sings.... "Smelly Cat" hahahahaha i love it!!!!  

ok thats it for now-and my brother got his license yesterday! yay for him and everyone else watch out......
